 *  Updated 12/16/04.
 *
 *  Thanks to Wojciech Bajon (http://histeria.pl/) for submitting code
 *  to handle relative links, which I hadn't considered. I modified his
 *  code a bit to handle normal HTTP links and MAILTO links. Also for
